Source: cnbiloop
Section: libs
Priority: extra
Maintainer: Michele Tavella <michele.tavella@epfl.ch>
Build-Depends: debhelper (>= 7), autotools-dev, libtobicore-dev, libxdffileio0-dev, libeegdev0-dev
Standards-Version: 3.8.3
Homepage: http://www.mtvl.org/cnbitk

Package: libcnbiloop
Section: libs
Architecture: any
Depends: ${shlibs:Depends}, ${misc:Depends}
Homepage: http://www.mtvl.org/cnbitk
Description: CNBI Toolkit Loop libraries
 Core components of the CNBI Toolkit. It provides basic functionalities such as 
 TCP/UDP networking, named pipes communication and EEG data tranfers. 
 It also provides high-level functionalities for acquiring/saving/streaming EEG
 data and BCI/protocol configuration. Last but not least, it provides all the
 applications required to run the BCI loop.

Package: libcnbiloop-dev
Section: libdevel
Architecture: any
Depends: libcnbiloop(= ${binary:Version}), ${misc:Depends}
Homepage: http://www.mtvl.org/cnbitk
Description: CNBI Toolkit Loop libraries
 Core components of the CNBI Toolkit. It provides basic functionalities such as 
 TCP/UDP networking, named pipes communication and EEG data tranfers. 
 It also provides high-level functionalities for acquiring/saving/streaming EEG
 data and BCI/protocol configuration. Last but not least, it provides all the
 applications required to run the BCI loop.
 .
 This package contains the files needed to compile and link programs which
 use cnbiloop.

